gw.api.web.team

Class CCTeamTreeViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.tree.AbstractLazyLoadingTreeNode
      • gw.api.web.team.CCTeamTreeViewModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CCTeamTreeViewGroupModel, CCTeamTreeViewSpecialEntryModel, CCTeamTreeViewUserModel

    public abstract class CCTeamTreeViewModel
extends AbstractLazyLoadingTreeNode
    Abstract superclass for model data stored on elements of the team tree. All models must know:
    • What to do when they are clicked treeElementClicked(pcf.api.Location)
    • How to identify themselves using equals/hashCode, so they can be recognized in the tree view cache
